# documented reasoning. Indexing operations carry
# #[expect(clippy::indexing_slicing)] with invariant documentation.
#
# Categories of as-casts present:
# - i64 -> f64 (precision loss): statistical aggregation (count, mean, variance)
# - u32 -> usize: graph node ID indexing (hot path, u32 always fits usize on 64-bit)
