# - f64 -> f32: intentional precision reduction for mixed-precision vector math
# - f64 -> i64: float truncation in numeric conversion functions
#
# Categories of direct indexing:
# - Graph algorithm node arrays: index validated by CSR graph bounds
# - Tuple access after length validation (snafu::ensure! checks)
# - Expression evaluation: index validated by compilation phase
# - HNSW vector search: layer/neighbor indices bounded by construction

